{"tid":405263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《基 本 法》 第 2 7 條 定 明 言 論 自 由 不 包 括 危 害 社 會 秩 序","createTime":"2017-09-18T16:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T17:04:58.000Z","uid":49388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc5eaaf77609aa706c3d6037d2f5582650f5e69","tid":405263,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:55:08.000Z","msg":"基本法第27條保障言論自由<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》第二十七條規定，香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。據了解，聯署的醫生諮詢法律意見後，認為醫委會專業守則限制醫生自我宣傳的條文，可能違反上述《基本法》保障港人的權利，並可能牴觸人權法，法律意見又指言論自由應只在涉及誹謗、危害國家安全或社會秩序時才受限制，醫生宣揚個人資料應不受此限。"},{"pid":"60673d2a2c589e59fb28259dc72c81560caed4b7","tid":405263,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:56:24.000Z","msg":"等睇對&quot;自由&quot;及&quot;權利&quot;釋法"},{"pid":"e84b4ef38623bee6dbc93a740fcb65d693a67e9c","tid":405263,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇對&quot;自由&quot;及&quot;權利&quot;釋法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b11c98d97e8a82fcae2ad1060dc89c5680d35e","tid":405263,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇對&quot;自由&quot;及&quot;權利&quot;釋法</blockquote><br />\n對不字釋法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae9166f25f76b181196dbe098f294c1049d8f14","tid":405263,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等睇對&quot;自由&quot;及&quot;權利&quot;釋法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跟住本地立法23條<br />\n(劇本)"},{"pid":"e9afa5af9893f0502533cb9979b9e8deb9986e7d","tid":405263,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:04:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等睇對&quot;自由&quot;及&quot;權利&quot;釋法</blockquote><br />\n對不字釋法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n釋法：不字係手誤寫多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}